de by focusing on non-equilibrium\nstatistical mechanics, which allows for a unified framing of problems as\ndifferent as the climate response to forcings, the effect of altering the\nboundary conditions or the coupling between geophysical flows, and the\nderivation of parametrizations for numerical models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2013 20:41:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Dec 2013 13:59:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Aug 2014 12:15:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
