y. Thus our source is a\ncandidate stellar-mass BHB with a supergiant companion or with a dwarf\ncompanion residing in a globular cluster. Our study supports that some\nlow-luminosity ULXs are supercritically accreting stellar-mass BHBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2013 20:59:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
